{"tid":886404,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[準備簽和約] 傳特朗普冀達成美中貿易協議 已要求內閣起草條款","createTime":"2018-11-02T05:28:15.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-02T10:39:05.000Z","uid":141151,"like":9,"dislike":23,"uniUserReply":51,"replies":[{"pid":"c7b701b67a6cc1b4c8c3d8dd2ccc9e4c9e3513d8","tid":886404,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-02T05:28:15.000Z","msg":"傳特朗普冀達成美中貿易協議 已要求內閣起草條款<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://china.hket.com/article/2199679/%E5%82%B3%E7%89%B9%E6%9C%97%E6%99%AE%E5%86%80%E9%81%94%E6%88%90%E7%BE%8E%E4%B8%AD%E8%B2%BF%E6%98%93%E5%8D%94%E8%AD%B0%20%E5%B7%B2%E8%A6%81%E6%B1%82%E5%85%A7%E9%96%A3%E8%B5%B7%E8%8D%89%E6%A2%9D%E6%AC%BE?mtc=30008\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fchina.hket.com%2Farticle%2F2199679%2F%25E5%2582%25B3%25E7%2589%25B9%25E6%259C%2597%25E6%2599%25AE%25E5%2586%2580%25E9%2581%2594%25E6%2588%2590%25E7%25BE%258E%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E8%25B2%25BF%25E6%2598%2593%25E5%258D%2594%25E8%25AD%25B0%2520%25E5%25B7%25B2%25E8%25A6%2581%25E6%25B1%2582%25E5%2585%25A7%25E9%2596%25A3%25E8%25B5%25B7%25E8%258D%2589%25E6%25A2%259D%25E6%25AC%25BE%3Fmtc%3D30008&d=w%2FTjyry8MbikErwJX0oMg10Hwm5JNK6yt%2FgZtp%2B4HOw%3D&h=f254ee42\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://china.hket.com/article/2199679/%E5%82%B3%E7%89%B9%E6%9C%97%E6%99%AE%E5%86%80%E9%81%94%E6%88%90%E7%BE%8E%E4%B8%AD%E8%B2%BF%E6%98%93%E5%8D%94%E8%AD%B0%20%E5%B7%B2%E8%A6%81%E6%B1%82%E5%85%A7%E9%96%A3%E8%B5%B7%E8%8D%89%E6%A2%9D%E6%AC%BE?mtc=30008</a><br />\n<br />\n中美元首通話後，兩國貿易戰再露出緩和曙光。彭博引述4名知情人士透露，美國總統特朗普希望在本月底的二十國集團（G20）峰會上，與中國國家主席習近平在達成貿易協議，已經要求美國要員開始起草潛在的條款。<br />\n<br />\n報道引述這些不願具名的人士稱，特朗普周四與習近平的通話，促成了與可能的美中協議的推進。在通話後，特朗普在Twitter表示，這是一次「長時間和非常好」的對話，雙方關於貿易的討論「正在順利進行之中」。<br />\n<br />\n特朗普又在密蘇里州的競選集會上表示，習近平希望達成「公平的貿易協議」。"},{"pid":"cd7353c0aec6ded6ea99891e9a0608f766c03330","tid":886404,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-02T05:29:03.000Z","msg":"Trump Asks Cabinet to Draft Possible Trade Deal With China<br />\n<br